title: IHC Triumphs Over Thousand Islands
text:
IHC Triumphs Over Thousand Islands   9, 2015 at 6:41 AM   9, 2015 at 10:12 AM EDT 
Immaculate Heart took down a previously undefeated Thousand Islands football squad Thursday night. The Cavaliers won the Section 3 Class C contest 29-26 Watch the video for highlights, plus action from a Norwood-Norfolk girls 'soccer win and a Parishville-Hopkinton win in boys' soccer.
